flowchart LR
    subgraph Data Producer
        ClientApp[Producer App] -->|1. Parse Event| Serializer[KafkaAvroSerializer]
    end

    subgraph Governance Core
        Registry[Schema Registry]
    end

    subgraph Messaging Fabric
        Broker[Kafka Cluster]
    end

    subgraph Data Consumer
        Deserializer[KafkaAvroDeserializer] -->|4. Parse Object| ConsumerApp[Consumer App]
    end

    %% Flow Steps
    Serializer ---|2. Register/Query Schema & Get ID| Registry
    Serializer -->|3. Write Avro Message: 5-byte header + binary payload| Broker
    Broker -->|4. Consume raw binary| Deserializer
    Deserializer ---|5. Lookup Schema ID| Registry

    style Registry fill:#f9f,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Broker fill:#bbf,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
